  "title": "Doctor / GP Clinic ( Preferred Location ) #HFQ",
  "description": "<p>The Role</p><p>1.⁠ ⁠Provide medical consultation and services to patients.</p><p>2.⁠ ⁠Prescribe medications and administer vaccinations as necessary.</p><p>3.⁠ ⁠Manage acute and chronic conditions related to the practice of Family Medicine</p><p>4.⁠ ⁠Perform minor office procedures, including but not limited to (T&S, I&D, FB removal, Excision)</p><p>5.⁠ ⁠Can opt to partake in other special projects including but not limited to onsite health screening, health talks, occupational health.</p><p></p><p>The Person</p><p>1.⁠ ⁠Bachelor’s degree in medicine and surgery (MBBS or MD)</p><p>2.⁠ ⁠Valid Practicing Certificate with SMC</p><p>3.⁠ ⁠Post graduate degree in Family Medicine (GDFM, MMed)</p><p>4.⁠ ⁠Other post graduate degrees can be considered (GDOM, MMED (Internal Medicine), GDGM)</p><p></p><p>Interested candidates please send a copy of your resume in MS Word to</p><p>Valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg<br /></p><p>EA Personnel:  Valerie Yong Kian Fung (R1103704)</p><p>Company Reg. No 199601303W</p><p>EA Licence No. 99C4599</p>",
